definition: to cross/to go over/to pass (time)/to celebrate (a holiday)/to live/to get along/excessively/too-

sentences.english: Second, it helps you avoid the pitfalls of premature optimization in your migration.
sentences.chinese: 其次，它可以帮助您避免迁移过程中的过早优化陷阱。

sentences.english: So the call about John’s untimely death was a fraud.
sentences.chinese: 这则关于约翰过早死亡的报道是欺诈新闻。

sentences.english: Malocclusion can be related to habits such as thumb sucking or premature loss of the deciduous (milk, baby) teeth.
sentences.chinese: 错颌畸形与一些习惯如允吸大拇指乳牙过早脱落有关。

sentences.english: Are you going gray too early?
sentences.chinese: 你的乌发是否过早的变白了？

sentences.english: 'It is too early to make conclusions now, ' Mr. Hommen said.
sentences.chinese: 霍曼说，现在下结论还为时过早。

sentences.english: Comes face to face with an adversary the brave victory, now judges true brave to be also too early.
sentences.chinese: 狭路相逢勇者胜，现在来判断真正的勇者还为时过早。

sentences.english: Don't constrict your breasts because of your shyness, and don't wear bra too early.
sentences.chinese: 不能因为害羞而束胸，也不能过早佩戴胸罩。

sentences.english: The reason for this premature descent will be clarified by the International Aviation Committee.
sentences.chinese: 而过早降落的原因还有待国际航空委员会的确认。

sentences.english: I think it premature for us to discuss the question of agency.
sentences.chinese: 我以为现在会商代庖代理题目为时过早。

sentences.english: U-en thinks the deer stone is no later than 7th century B. C.
sentences.chinese: 乌恩把鹿石年代下限定在公元前7世纪失之过早。

sentences.english: Depriving him of the breast, could lead to serious problems in his personality development.
sentences.chinese: 过早断奶，会对他的人格发展造成严重影响。

sentences.english: Nor could I affect the early judgments on my so-called legacy.
sentences.chinese: 我也无法左右对我的所谓的遗产的过早评价。

sentences.english: A recent study finds C-sections may be a contributing to babies being born too early.
sentences.chinese: 最近一项研究发现剖腹产使婴儿过早出生。

sentences.english: Wuhan will use the earlier, called "premature."
sentences.chinese: 武汉人将用早点，称为“过早”。

sentences.english: But it's far too early to talk about a hard landing in China.
sentences.chinese: 但是这还为时过早谈一谈在中国硬着陆。

sentences.english: Enhances skin repiratory ability and prevent premature aging of the skin.
sentences.chinese: 防止过早出现衰老现象，保持青春活力。
